{"tid":1564715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由有公信力既人物 去為各個前線手足眾籌","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:55:12.000Z","uid":61886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9678e0e2168977d45869e263f8bb336e290445","tid":1564715,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:18:28.000Z","msg":"事緣今日見到報導有位手足連學費都交唔到<br />\n<br />\n我自己有個概念<br />\n<br />\n因為其實好多前線手足都有唔同既金錢需要<br />\n可能係升學、住屋、裝備、甚至係流亡既生活費<br />\n<br />\n會唔會可以有有公信力既人物<br />\n可能係議員、媒體、機構<br />\n聯絡到有需要既手足<br />\n直接開不同既眾籌項目 (好似登報咁)<br />\n每個項目寫返係咩需要<br />\n唔似612基金咁收晒一大筆錢再慢慢批<br />\n而係每位手足有獨立既眾籌<br />\n籌夠數就截<br />\n再轉交比相關既手足<br />\n<br />\n好處係直接可以送到手足手上<br />\n唔使經繁複既批核程序<br />\n亦唔會捐左啲錢唔知用左去邊<br />\n<br />\n大家brainstorm下可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ba5120870092b277ad8d9537cdfafc35345765","tid":1564715,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zxXzKWa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzxXzKWa.jpg&h=c7c324a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c27f302ac3a9a1f3094451904306cb9ad915502","tid":1564715,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:19:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3